---
import MainLayout from "~/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { getMetadata } from "~/lib/constants";

const { name, links } = getMetadata();
const lastUpdated = "February 20, 2025";
---

<MainLayout
  title={`Privacy Policy | ${name}`}
  description="Information about how we collect, use and protect your personal data."
>
  <main class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 xl:px-10 py-20">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <a
        href="/en"
        class="text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors"
      >
        ‚Üê Back to home
      </a>
    </div>

    <article class="prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p>
        At <strong>{name}</strong> we take the privacy of our users very seriously. This
        policy explains what personal data we collect, for what purpose, and how we protect
        it, in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and Spanish
        data protection law.
      </p>

      <h2>1. Data Controller</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Name:</strong> {name}</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={links.email}>gubaupol@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href={links.website} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{links.website}</a></li>
        <li><strong>Location:</strong> Barcelona, Spain</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following types of data:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Contact data:</strong> name, email address, phone number and message, when
          you voluntarily provide them through our contact form or WhatsApp.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Browsing data:</strong> IP address, browser type, pages visited and time
          spent, collected anonymously via technical and analytical cookies.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
      <p>We use your data to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to your enquiries and quote requests.</li>
        <li>Manage the commercial relationship arising from the provision of our services.</li>
        <li>Send you information about our services, if you have given us your explicit consent.</li>
        <li>Improve the performance and user experience of the website.</li>
        <li>Comply with applicable legal obligations.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Performance of a contract</strong> or pre-contractual measures.</li>
        <li><strong>Consent</strong> of the data subject (contact form, subscriptions).</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> in improving our services and communications.</li>
        <li><strong>Compliance with legal obligations.</strong></li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We will retain your data for as long as necessary for the purpose for which it was
        collected, or while a contractual relationship exists, and in any case for the
        periods established by applicable legislation.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Recipients</h2>
      <p>
        We do not share your data with third parties, except where legally required or where
        necessary for the provision of the service (e.g., web hosting providers or
        communication tools). All providers offer adequate data protection guarantees.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You may exercise the following rights at any time by contacting{" "}
        <a href={links.email}>gubaupol@gmail.com</a>:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Access:</strong> find out what data we process about you.</li>
        <li><strong>Rectification:</strong> correct inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
        <li><strong>Erasure:</strong> request deletion of your data.</li>
        <li><strong>Objection:</strong> object to the processing of your data.</li>
        <li><strong>Restriction:</strong> request restriction of processing.</li>
        <li><strong>Portability:</strong> receive your data in a structured format.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency
        (<a href="https://www.aepd.es" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aepd.es</a>).
      </p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>
      <p>
        We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your data
        against unauthorised access, loss, alteration or disclosure.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update this policy at any time. The current version will
        always be available on this page with the date of the last update.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions related to this privacy policy, you can contact us at{" "}
        <a href={links.email}>gubaupol@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
